Steven Gerrard and Phil Jagielka released 96 red balloons at the 26th Hillsborough memorial service at Anfield . 
  The 96 Liverpool fans who died at the disaster were honoured at the service . 
  Brendan Rodgers and the entire Liverpool squad attended the memorial service . 
  Everton manager Roberto Martinez was also present at the memorial . 
  The service marked the anniversary of the Hillsborough disaster . 
 